---
title: Hoisin Tofu & Veggie Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: Behind every great stir-fry, there's got to be a great sauce! This one has hoisin, brown sugar, lime zest and soy sauce – it's a knockout. Toss it through tofu and a medley of veggies for a fast and easy weeknight winner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nz-tofu-hoisin-stir-fry-0a939819.jpg
